  "reviews": "\u201cFearless Fantasy Shows No Fear In Its Condensed RPG Design\u201d<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2014/05/03/fearless-fantasy-shows-no-fear-in-its-condensed-rpg-design/83294/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Hardcore Gamer</a><br><br>\u201cIt\u2019s a strange, silly game that just so happens to also have a unique and unexpectedly challenging battle system.\u201d<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.vgblogger.com/indie-quickie-fearless-fantasy/26357/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >VGBlogger</a><br><br>\u201cA compact adventure with a focus on turn-based skill, a notion as unique as the whole game itself.\u201d<br>9/10 \u2013 <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.gamegrin.com/reviews/fearless-fantasy-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >GameGrin</a><br>",
